item.title: Stiga Combi 50 SQ B Lawn Mower
item.dc:creator: chedemo
item.content:encoded:
The Combi 50 SEQ B is a versatile premium self-propelled lawnmower with a 163cc Briggs & Stratton 625IS Series InStart electric start engine and a robust steel body with a powder coated paint finish for longevity. You can collect clippings into the 70 litre grass collector, or if the grass is longer remove the collector and rear discharge. You can simply insert the mulching plug and drive in Multiclip mode or insert the mulching plug and remove the deck guard for side discharge.
Easily operated by a single lever, the 48cm/19" deck has a choice of 5 cutting height positions ranging from 25 to 65mm and will produce a great finish on your lawn whatever the conditions.
Mulching is by far the easiest way to cut your grass and the innovative blade and deck design also makes the lawnmower quieter. The Stiga Multiclip system cuts and recuts the grass into tiny pieces that simply wilt away, returning valuable nutrients to the soil to encourage beautiful green growth. You dont need to rake up the clippings or empty a collector, which means you can cut the grass about 30% faster compared to a collecting mower.

• Briggs & Stratton 625 Easy Start engine 2.27kW
  • 48cm cutting width
  • 4-in-1 - Collect, mulch, Rear discharge, side discharge
  • 5 Height of cut settings: 25-65mm
  • Self-propelled drive

item.title: Bosch Rotak 320 ER Electric Rotary Lawnmower
item.dc:creator: chedemo
item.content:encoded: The high speed 1200 Watt motor and innovative gear set on the Rotak 320 ER work together to give torque when needed. When the going gets tough, the torque automatically increases to work more powerfully, even under difficult conditions. Cutting longer or damp grass can be undertaken with confidence, thanks to the PowerDrive motor. Height of cut adjustment The Rotak 320 ER features a simple-to-use, tool-free 3-position height of cut adjustment which ranges from 20 to 60mm (3 settings). A handy and useful indicator helps you select different cutting heights by simply positioning the front or rear axles into the appropriate slot to suit. Cable length With 10 metres of cable you can move around the garden freely--perfect for small lawns. Lightweight and easy to carry and store Weighing only 6.8kg the Rotak 320 ER is extremely easy to use, and with an integrated carry handle and fold-down handles it is very easy to move and store. Grassbox capacity The Rotak 320ER lawnmower comes complete with a 31 litre grassbox which means you wont have to spend as much time emptying grass cuttings--so more time can be spent gardening.
